s he also sold the plymouth arena to usa hockey karmanos his compuware partner thewes and former player jim rutherford purchased the hartford whalers in  for  million at the time they had committed to keeping the team in hartford for at least four years connecticuts thengovernor lowell p weicker announced that karmanos would be critical for the team to stay in hartford weicker later became a member of the compuware board of directors karmanos was unable to sell  season tickets in hartford during the – nhl season and announced the team would leave hartford before a new city had been found if the whalers were unable to sell  season tickets for the – season even though they surpassed  season tickets in  the team was moved to raleigh north carolina and renamed the carolina hurricanes following the – season as a result karmanos is still reviled by many people in connecticut the hurricanes went on to win the stanley cup in  with karmanos eagerly donning his skates hoisting the cup and skating around with it briefly after the game win for his day with the cup he brought it to compuware hq in detroit and allowed employees to get their photo taken individually with the cup karmanos gale force holdings has a subsidiary dedicated to the nhl hurricanes holdings llc which includes the hurricanes and their stadium pnc arena the holdings also include the hurricaness echl affiliate florida everblades along with stadium germain arena in fort myers florida karmanos received the lester patrick trophy for outstanding service to hockey after the – season the bill long award in  for services to the ontario hockey league and was inducted to the united states hockey hall of fame in  he was inducted to the hockey hall of fame in the builder category in  karmanos also sponsors youth hockey programs in michigan under his backing karmanos youth hockey teams have accumulated numerous state national and international tournaments personal lifeedit karmanos donated money to the michigan cancer foundation which was renamed the barbara ann karmanos cancer institute in  in memory of his first wife barbara ann karmanos who died of breast cancer in  in addition to three children with barbara karmanos has four others with current wife danialle and nine grandchildren referencesedit    adams alan   people of power and influence the hockey news    accessdate requires url help  httpwwwcrainsdetroitcomarticleblogthingsyoumaynotknowaboutpetekarmanosjrwhoretiresfrom  a b c hurricanes karmanos a true hockey builder nhlcom  karmanos stepping down as compuware corps ceo june     a golden parachute will gently carry pete karmanos into retirement march     departure of directors or certain officers september     httpwwwcrainsdetroitcomarticlenewspeterkarmanosstartsnewcompanymaddogtechnology  mcmann aaron february   its official ontario hockey league approves plymouth whalers move to flint mlivecom the flint journal retrieved february     mcmann aaron march   flint firebirds unveiled as name for flints new ohl team mlivecom the flint journal retrieved march     usah foundation completes compuware arena purchase  whalers sold to stay in hartford  a b peter karmanos jr ceo  owner  governor  hanley christine april   hartford rally to save the whale a soso event boca raton news p b   espn  rating nhl moves past present and future  nhl  a b stanley cup journal  peter karmanos jr  peter karmanos jr  builder category external linksedit compuware web site carolina hurricanes  official nhl web site pete karmanos personal blog v t e carolina hurricanes formerly the new englandhartford whalers founded in  based in raleigh north carolina franchise team general managers coaches players captains draft picks expansion draft seasons current season history records award winners retired numbers personnel owners peter karmanos jr general manager ron francis head coach bill peters team captain vacant current roster arenas greensboro coliseum pnc arena affiliates ahl charlotte checkers echl florid